@startuml S4 - Monitoring Progress

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam maxmessagesize 100
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ArrowColor #000000
skinparam BorderColor #000000
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #000000
skinparam ParticipantFontColor #000000
skinparam ActorBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam ActorBorderColor #000000
skinparam ActorFontColor #000000
skinparam DatabaseBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam DatabaseBorderColor #000000
skinparam DatabaseFontColor #000000
skinparam BoxBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam BoxBorderColor #000000
skinparam BoxFontColor #000000
skinparam LifeLineBorderColor #000000
skinparam LifeLineBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam NoteBorderColor #000000
skinparam NoteFontColor #000000

actor Mahasiswa
actor Dosen
participant "S4. Monitoring Progress" as MonitorProgress
database "DS3: Progress (ProgressMateri)" as DBProgress
database "DS2: Tugas" as DBTugas

== Mahasiswa Membaca / Mengakses Materi ==

Mahasiswa -> MonitorProgress : Buka / download modul ajar
MonitorProgress -> DBProgress : Cek apakah materi sudah pernah diakses
DBProgress --> MonitorProgress : Status progress
alt Belum pernah diakses
    MonitorProgress -> DBProgress : Insert ProgressMateri (status: sudah, tanggalAkses: now)
else Sudah pernah diakses
    MonitorProgress -> DBProgress : Update tanggalAkses
end
DBProgress --> MonitorProgress : Progress tersimpan
MonitorProgress --> Mahasiswa : Kirim sinyal materi telah dibaca (status diperbarui)

== Mahasiswa Melihat Progress Materi ==

Mahasiswa -> MonitorProgress : Minta ringkasan progress per mata kuliah
MonitorProgress -> DBProgress : Hitung total materi vs sudah diakses
DBProgress --> MonitorProgress : { total, completed, percentage }
MonitorProgress --> Mahasiswa : Tampilkan persentase progress materi

== Dosen Memantau Progress Mahasiswa ==

DBTugas -> MonitorProgress : Info tugas telah selesai dikumpulkan
MonitorProgress -> DBProgress : Ambil progress materi per mahasiswa
DBProgress --> MonitorProgress : Data progress semua mahasiswa
MonitorProgress --> Dosen : Kirim informasi progress mahasiswa

== Dashboard Menampilkan Progress ==

Mahasiswa -> MonitorProgress : Buka dashboard
MonitorProgress -> DBProgress : Hitung tugas selesai / total tugas
MonitorProgress -> DBProgress : Hitung materi diakses / total materi
DBProgress --> MonitorProgress : Persentase progress keseluruhan
MonitorProgress --> Mahasiswa : Tampilkan progress bar di dashboard

@enduml
